 Check if my Windows 10 image is corrupted
------------------------------------------

  
Open Powershell, and execute:  
  
PS H:\\> Get-FileHash -Path 'C:\\Users\\xxxxxxx\\Downloads\\en-gb\_windows\_10\_multi-edition\_vl\_version\_1709\_updated\_dec\_2017\_x64\_dvd\_100406231.iso' -Algorithm SHA1
